          "date": "2014-06-16 18:07:51.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-3639 osd: check real OI files for local FID lookup",
        "message": "LU-3639 osd: check real OI files for local FID lookup\n\nFor the case of upgrading to Lustre-2.x (x >= 4),\nthere will be local FID in LMA and OI mapping for\nthe local object, and then when downgrade back to\nLustre-2.y (y <= 3), the osd_fid_lookup will use\nlocal FID to (NOT the original IGIF FID) call the\nosd_oi_lookup(), then we need to check the real OI\nfiles to avoid to return -ENOENT.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I85a452f23e64a26a27fb6145562508e1e4da2062\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_3"
    }
  },
